snippet.title: UW Department of Medicine
snippet.description:
This is the official YouTube channel of the University of Wisconsin-Madison Department of Medicine. The Department of Medicine is the largest academic department at UW-Madison, and our activities span 11 clinical areas, educational programs for every stage of medical careers, and a wide range of basic, translational, clinical, and population health research. 

The Department of Medicine advances the health of the people of Wisconsin and beyond. With an emphasis on excellence and equity, department members are devoted to leadership and innovation. We work together to heal, discover, and train. 

Social media statement: https://www.medicine.wisc.edu/department-medicine/social-media-statement
